en_question:
 A company is responsible for transporting along four shipping routes. The known information is as follows: 1. The origin and destination cities for each route and the number of sailings per day are shown in Table 3-21. 2.The sailing times between each pair of cities are shown in Table 3-22. 3.The same type of ship is used for all routes, and each loading and unloading operation takes 1 day. Question: What is the minimum number of ships the company must deploy in order to meet the transportation requirements on all routes? 

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 3-21: Route Information}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|c|c|c}
        \toprule
        Route & Origin City & Destination City & Sailings per Day \\
        \midrule
        1 & E & D & 3 \\
        2 & B & C & 2 \\
        3 & A & F & 1 \\
        4 & D & B & 1 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 3-22: Sailing Times Between Cities (in days)}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|cccccc}
        \toprule
        From$\backslash$To & A & B & C & D & E & F \\
        \midrule
        A & 0 & 1 & 2 & 14 & 7 & 7 \\
        B & 1 & 0 & 3 & 13 & 8 & 8 \\
        C & 2 & 3 & 0 & 15 & 5 & 5 \\
        D & 14 & 13 & 15 & 0 & 17 & 20 \\
        E & 7 & 8 & 5 & 17 & 0 & 3 \\
        F & 7 & 8 & 5 & 20 & 3 & 0 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

cn_question:
    某公司承担 4 条航线的运输任务，已知：
\begin{enumerate}
    \item 各条航线的起点城市和终点城市及每天的航班数（见表 3-21）。
    \item 各城市间的航行时间（见表 3-22）。
    \item 所有航线都使用同一种船只，每次装船和卸船时间均为 1 天。
\end{enumerate}
问该公司至少应配备多少条船才能满足所有航线运输的需要？

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{各航线信息（表 3-21）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|c|c|c}
        \toprule
        航线 & 起点城市 & 终点城市 & 每天航班数量 \\
        \midrule
        1 & E & D & 3 \\
        2 & B & C & 2 \\
        3 & A & F & 1 \\
        4 & D & B & 1 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{各城市间的航行时间（天）（表 3-22）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|cccccc}
        \toprule
        从$\backslash$至 & A & B & C & D & E & F \\
        \midrule
        A & 0 & 1 & 2 & 14 & 7 & 7 \\
        B & 1 & 0 & 3 & 13 & 8 & 8 \\
        C & 2 & 3 & 0 & 15 & 5 & 5 \\
        D & 14 & 13 & 15 & 0 & 17 & 20 \\
        E & 7 & 8 & 5 & 17 & 0 & 3 \\
        F & 7 & 8 & 5 & 20 & 3 & 0 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}
